<div class="masthead">
  <div class="col-lg-4 col-lg-offset-4 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2 col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1">
    <p class="program"> CALFRESH & MEDI-CAL</p>
  </div>
</div>
<form name="first_income_doc" action="/first_income_doc" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data" class="form col-lg-4 col-lg-offset-4 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2 col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1">
  <h3>If you have one, upload an income document.</h3>
  <div class="form-group">
    <p>Every Calfresh applicant needs to provide proof of income. Acceptable income documents include:
      <ul>
        <li>Paystubs</li>
        <li>Bank statements</li>
        <li>Last year's tax return</li>
        <li>Written and signed statements</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
    <p>If you don't have proof of income on hand, that's ok. Skip this step for now, and try to locate income documents in advance of your interview.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="form-group file-group">
    <label for="income">Upload Document</label>
    <input type="file" name="income" autofocus="autofocus"></input>
  </div>
  <h5 class="or" style="text-align:center">or</h5>
  <a class="btn skip form-button-link-solo" href="/first_expense_doc">Skip</a>
  <div class="page-footer" style="display:none">
    <input class="btn next-step" type="submit" value="Submit Document">
  </div>
</form>
<script>
  $('.btn').button();
  $(function() {
     $("input:file").change(function () {
       $(".page-footer").removeAttr("style");
       $(".or").hide();
       $(".skip").hide();
     });
  });
</script>
